StringAttributes

public StringAttributes(boolean caseSensitive)
Creates a new Stringattributes object with the specified case sensitivity. When case sensitivity is set to false, all attribute names are forced to lower case.

Parameters:
caseSensitive - false forces attribute names to lower case.
